{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ピタゴラスの定理の証明","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/MathML_Pythagorean_Theorem","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>ピタゴラスの定理を証明します。</p>\n<p><strong>命題</strong>: 直角三角形では、斜辺の 2 乗は他の 2 辺の 2 乗の和に等しい。</p>\n<p>すなわち、 a と b を脚とし、c を斜辺とすると、\n  <math>\n    \n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>a </mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n      <mo>+ </mo>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>b </mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n      <mo>= </mo>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>c </mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </math>\n</p>\n<p><strong>証明:</strong> 大きな正方形の面積は、内側の正方形の面積（斜辺の 2 乗）に 4 つの三角形の面積を加えたものに等しいことを示すことで、定理を代数的に証明することができます。</p>\n<p>\n  <math>\n    <mtable columnalign=\"right center left\">\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>( </mo>\n              <mi>a </mi>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <mi>b </mi>\n              <mo>) </mo>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>2 </mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <mo>= </mo>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>c </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mn>4 </mn>\n          <mo>⋅ </mo>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1 </mn>\n            <mn>2 </mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mi>a </mi>\n          <mi>b </mi>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>a </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mn>2 </mn>\n          <mi>a </mi>\n          <mi>b </mi>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>b </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <mo>= </mo>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>c </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mn>2 </mn>\n          <mi>a </mi>\n          <mi>b</mi>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>a </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>b </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <mo>= </mo>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>c </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n    </mtable>\n  </math>\n</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"ピタゴラスの定理を証明します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Proving the Pythagorean theorem","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML Pythagorean Theorem","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Preuve du théorème de Pythagore","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Доказательство теоремы Пифагора","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/examples/mathml_pythagorean_theorem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/examples/mathml_pythagorean_theorem/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Examples","title":"例"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/MathML_Pythagorean_Theorem","title":"ピタゴラスの定理の証明"}],"pageTitle":"ピタゴラスの定理の証明 - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}